®PROCESS;
<param> <name>The name of the parameter as used a key-value pair.</name> <desc>A natural-language description of the parameter.</desc> <status> The requirements status of the record. Should be one of: - required - recommended - optional - deprecated - obsolete </status> </param>
The registrant can register more than one parameter at a time, each contained in a separate <record/> element.
